  version: {{ version }}

source:

    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - cmake
    - ninja
    - pkgconfig  # [not win]

  commands:
    - test -f ${PREFIX}/share/cmake/ignition-cmake{{ major_version }}/ignition-cmake{{ major_version }}-config.cmake  # [not win]
